People List -- commands 
    1 – to input a person 
        » Name, Age, Status 
    2 – to delete a person 
        » Name 
    3 – to show the current list of info 
    4 – to quit 
    
Your program keeps a counter,which indicates how many elements are in the list 
According to the command, the program 
    1 – insert an element at the position indicated by counter and increase the counter 
    2 – delete the element with the given name 
        - to keep all the elements together, copy the last one to the deleted one and decrease the counter 
    3 – show all the elements, from position zero to counter-1 
    4 - quit
